Class Swim

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • Workout
        • Swim

  • public class Swim
extends Workout
    Subclass of Workout, grandchild of Activity. Creates workouts of type Swim, which include number of laps, and swimming style.
    Author:
    Ana J. Garcia
    See Also:
    Workout, Activity
